  "description": "Extra Content to the Race mod CreRaces!",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">CreRaces Extras is being revived and from b1.1+ will now be showcasing how to add custom content to CreRaces as a Modpack or Mod developer!</span></span></p>\n<p>Welcome to CreRaces Extra! This mod will proved extra content to the Race mod CreRaces!</p>\n<p>With this mod's revival I also aim to showcase what you yourself as an individual or modpack/mod developer can add to the <a title=\"CreRaces\" href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/creraces\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">base</a> mod as custom content!<br /><a title=\"Join the Discord!\" href=\"https://discord.gg/QagkwvSWtC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/844129861861376042?label=Join%20the%20Discord%21&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=FFFFFF\" alt=\"https://discord.gg/QagkwvSWtC\" width=\"181\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p>Currently it shows how to add:</p>\n<p><em>- New Scaling items</em></p>\n<p><em>- more soon...<br /><br /></em></p>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Supported Versions:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><i><strong>1.7.10:</strong>&nbsp;N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.12.2:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.14.4:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.15.2:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><strong>1.16.5: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.17.1: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.18.2:</strong>&nbsp;LTS: <em>\"Long Term Support\"</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong> 1.19.2:</strong><em>&nbsp;</em>STS:<em> \"Short Term Support\"&nbsp;</em></i></p>\n<p><strong>1.19.4: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></p>\n<p><em><strong>1.20.1: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;None</em></p>\n<p><i><em>Do note that this is the plan but things may change overtime!</em></i></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Guide:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>1. <b>coming soon...</b></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Credits:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><em><strong>Developers:</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3&nbsp;\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><em>Textures:</em></strong></p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a> &amp; other</em></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n<p><em>Made by: <a title=\"mc_jojo3\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></em></p>",
